snippet.title: Sushi For Robots - Out Now Trailer
snippet.description:
Sushi for Robots is a whimsical, low pressure cooking puzzle game which invites you to serve antsy robots the sushi of their dreams.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2160240
Itchio: https://ludipe.itch.io/sushi-for-robots
